{"content": "I need to multiply a87 \u00d7 548 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert a87 (base 11) to base 10**\n- a87\u2081\u2081 = 10\u00d711\u00b2 + 8\u00d711\u00b9 + 7\u00d711\u2070\n- = 10\u00d7121 + 8\u00d711 + 7\u00d71\n- = 1210 + 88 + 7\n- = 1305\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 548 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 548\u2081\u2081 = 5\u00d711\u00b2 + 4\u00d711\u00b9 + 8\u00d711\u2070\n- = 5\u00d7121 + 4\u00d711 + 8\u00d71\n- = 605 + 44 + 8\n- = 657\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 1305 \u00d7 657 = 857,385\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 857,385 back to base 11**\n- 857385 \u00f7 11 = 77944 R 1\n- 77944 \u00f7 11 = 7086 R 2\n- 7086 \u00f7 11 = 644 R 2\n- 644 \u00f7 11 = 58 R 6\n- 58 \u00f7 11 = 5 R 3\n- 5 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 5\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 536221\n\n**Answer: 536221**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 394}